0.text: There is a magic sword in the cave. Can you get it? Although you can follow the instructions given, they are not in order. Write them in the correct order.
0.ssml: <speak><prosody rate='slow'>There is a magic sword in the cave. Can you get it? Although you can follow the instructions given, they are not in order. Write them in the correct order.</prosody></speak>

1.text: • Jump over the fence again and walk slowly through the tunnel.
1.ssml: <speak><prosody rate='slow'>Jump over the fence again and walk slowly through the tunnel.</prosody></speak>

2.text: • Start your journey from A and walk along the road.
2.ssml: <speak><prosody rate='slow'>Start your journey from A and walk along the road.</prosody></speak>

3.text: • Next, climb up the hill and come down.

4.text: • Then, you can see a big bridge and walk over it.

5.text: • After that, go through the dark forest.

6.text: • Great! Now, the magic sword is yours.
6.ssml: <speak><prosody rate='slow'>Great! Now, the magic sword is yours.</prosody></speak>

7.text: • Then, jump over the fence and run across the field.

8.text: • After that, walk around the farm and go under the little bridge.
